text: §436E-4  Exemptions.  A licensed acupuncturist of another state or country for demonstrations or lectures to be given at acupuncture or medical society meetings or at acupuncture schools shall be exempt from licensing procedures set forth in this chapter. [L 1985, c 214, pt of §1; am L 1989, c 180, §1]
